CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. 15 reads: "Young Fry Step Out in Colorful Fashion Show! - Walter, Marva, Melvin Williams - Portions of accompanying article reads: "Some of Pittsburgh's most delightful younger set members set a fast pace of fashions at the A. Leo Weil School Friday night, when the Centre Avenue Community Club presented a happy revue, complete with a singing, dancing prelude to styles..."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Walter Williams and Melvin Williams, standing on either side of Marva Williams wearing light colored knee length dress with shawl, standing on stage in A. Leo Weil school for Community Club sponsored Fashion Show
